0.2 Ambiguity Elimination
0.2.1 Sources of Ambiguity
Stakeholder language vs system reality
Implicit assumptions and tribal knowledge
0.2.2 Techniques to Surface Ambiguity
Rule decomposition
Scenario expansion
Edge-case interrogation
0.2.3 Writing to Eliminate Interpretation
Deterministic language standards
One-requirement–one-behavior principle
