Identifying high-risk ambiguous areas
Prioritizing clarification based on SLA and security impact
0.2.5 Ambiguity in Agile Environments
Managing evolving requirements without losing precision
Preventing “we’ll figure it out later” failures
0.3 Ops-First Responsibility
0.3.1 Understanding Operations Reality
24×7 support constraints
Shift-based execution and handovers
0.3.2 Designing for the 2 AM Scenario
Decision-making under fatigue
Reduced context availability
0.3.3 Protecting Operations from Bad Design
Identifying requirements that overload ops
Automation vs manual control trade-offs
